Actor Brad Pitt appeared extremely thin as he walked down the street here. Clad in white long-sleeved shirt and jeans, paired with brown shoes and sunglasses, the 53-year-old actor was photographed, while taking a stroll through one of the streets in LA.There are reports doing the rounds that Pitt has lost weight for his new film, &#8216;Ad Astra&#8217;, which will begin filming in July. The sci-fi film tells a story of an autistic engineer who travels to space in order to look for his father who is missing after trying to find a new extra-terrestrial life in Neptune.James Gray has been set to write and direct the movie.This article first appeared on Times of India 